# --- Large generated / downloaded map data (regenerate with tools/) ---
# State basemap extracts (hundreds of MB each)
/mapdata/
# Contents rather than the directory itself: git cannot re-include a file whose
# parent directory is excluded, and the starter pack below has to ship.
/public/mapdata/*
# The one exception — a whole-US basemap at low zoom, ~11 MB, bundled so a fresh
# install opens on a real map instead of an empty screen. Built by
# `src-tauri/src/bin/build-pack.rs`; see docs/prebuilt-packs.md.
!/public/mapdata/starter.pmtiles
# Offline elevation tile pyramid (~1 GB per state)
/public/dem/

# Downloaded go-pmtiles binary (fetch from GitHub releases)
/tools/pmtiles
/tools/*.tar.gz
# Bundled sidecar binaries (large; provisioned from tools/pmtiles per platform)
/src-tauri/binaries/

# Local region config (copy from region.example.json) — keep your region private
/public/region.json
